OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has announced
OL,7,Fa national independent review into
OL,8,Fmaternity services.
OL,10,FMothers-to-be in Stranraer and the
OL,11,Fsurrounding area have to travel more
OL,12,Fthan 70 miles to Dumfries to give
OL,13,Fbirth in a hospital.
OL,15,FHealth Secretary Angela Constance said
OL,16,Fthe review will listen to women and
OL,17,Ffamilies in Wigtownshire, as well as
OL,18,Flocal health professionals.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
