OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FStranraer mother Jenna Henry told ITV
OL,7,FBorder she is considering moving away
OL,8,Ffrom the town due to a lack of local
OL,9,Fmaternity care.
OL,11,FShe had to make the journey to the
OL,12,FDumfries and Galloway Royal Infirmary
OL,13,Fwhile in labour with her son Theo in
OL,14,FDecember 2024.
OL,16,FShe said: "I just remember sitting in
OL,17,Fthe back of my auntie's car,
OL,18,Fbreathing. I don't know what to think.
OL,19,FAm I going to get there in time? Am I
OL,20,Fgoing to have a baby in this car right
OL,21,Fnow or am I going to make it?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,F"Sometimes I actually go through the
OL,7,Fprocess of thinking, is this where I
OL,8,Fwant to live? Is it really a place
OL,9,Fthat you want to go through and you've
OL,10,Fgot everything at your front door? No,
OL,11,Fyou don't have that. So personally I
OL,12,Fwould want to move away from
OL,13,FStranraer."
OL,15,FBabies haven't been delivered at the
OL,16,Flocal Galloway Community Hospital
OL,17,Fsince 2018, when the birthing unit
OL,18,Fclosed.
OL,20,FInstead women are required to travel
OL,21,Fon the A75 to hospital in Dumfries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
