PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FCampaigner Claire Fleming has warned
OL,7,Fthe situation is an 'accident waiting
OL,8,Fto happen'
OL,10,FThe review into maternity services in
OL,11,FScotland will be led by Christina
OL,12,FMcCourt, Professor of Maternal and
OL,13,FChild Health at City St George's
OL,14,FUniversity of London.
OL,16,FIt is expected to begin after the
OL,17,Fsummer and be completed within nine
OL,18,Fmonths.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FMs Constance said: "Professor McCourt
OL,7,Fwill engage with women, families,
OL,8,Fpatient groups, clinicians, midwives,
OL,9,Fnurses and the wider maternity
OL,10,Fworkforce across Scotland - including
OL,11,Fin Caithness and Wigtownshire. It is
OL,12,Fessential that the voices of those
OL,13,Freceiving and delivering care are
OL,14,Fheard directly throughout this
OL,15,Fprocess."
OL,17,FShe added: "Every woman in Scotland
OL,18,Fdeserves safe, compassionate and high-
OL,19,Fquality maternity care, regardless of
OL,20,Fwhere she lives.
OL,26,@nD@TOUwD@IO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
