OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FClaire Fleming said: "My biggest fear
OL,7,Fis that there's going to be a loss of
OL,8,Fa mum or a baby or both on that road.
OL,9,FI think it's stressful enough for the
OL,10,Fpartner or whoever is driving them
OL,11,Fdown there, it's hard to concentrate
OL,12,Fif you've got someone in labour in the
OL,13,Ffront seat with you. I think it's an
OL,14,Faccident waiting to happen.
OL,16,F"We've already had reviews down here,
OL,17,Fwe've had people that have come and
OL,18,Flooked at it and they've said no
OL,19,Fthat's not acceptable but nothing
OL,20,Fchanged after that either."
OL,26,@nD@VOUxD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
