PN,32507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781395390
OL,3,CWigtownshire maternity services to be
OL,4,Cexamined in national review
OL,6,FProfessor McCourt said: "Positive
OL,7,Fmaternity experiences and outcomes are
OL,8,Fvital for our health and wellbeing. I
OL,9,Flook forward to listening and learning
OL,10,Ffrom families and communities across
OL,11,FScotland, as well as from those who
OL,12,Fprovide dedicated care in our NHS.
OL,13,FThis will help draw out lessons for
OL,14,Fmaternity and neonatal services and
OL,15,Fcontribute to ensuring the best
OL,16,Fpossible care for all."
OL,26,@nD@YOU
